title: Rename a class and its file
message_prompt: Rename SearchBox to Navigation - the file and the class.
message_edit:
I will rename the file `SearchBox.js` to `Navigation.js` and update the class name from `SearchBox` to `Navigation`.

Steps:
1. Rename the file `SearchBox.js` to `Navigation.js`.
2. Replace the class name `SearchBox` with `Navigation` in the `Navigation.js` file.
3. Update the import statement in `App.js` to reflect the new file and class name.
